Modern market crash in 4 easy steps:
1. Investors redeem from hedge funds
2. Funds sell largest, most liquid positions ($AAPL, $AMZN, etc) to meet redemptions
3. Selling pushes market down
4. Repeat

Unlike 2001/2008 the fundamentals are still good.
